      "## The \"Post and Pray\" Trap",
      "When an HR leader is forced into recruiting, a pattern emerges almost instantly. You post the job. You hope. You wait for applications to roll in. Two weeks later, you have a folder of 47 resumes, and you realize 43 of them do not understand the role at all.",
